COMPATIBILITY
 * shorten files
 * byte alignment
 * block encryption API (for things like TrueCrypt or dm-crypt)
 * exported API (libpeng)

OPTIMIZATION
 * threads
 * bit ordering

LUXURY
 * store parameters with enc file
 * integrity checks

DOCUMENTATION
 * doxygen

DEBUG
 * verbosity>2 displays keys
 * debug system

QUESTIONABLE
 X CBC(X-P-X)

SECURITY
